      "note": "description",
      "abstract": "Prohibits counties from permitting or allowing retention and detention ponds to be constructed except under certain conditions.  Requires the Department of Health to inspect retention and detention ponds statewide.  Establishes certain safety requirements.  Appropriates funds."
